{
  "stem": "18778.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And there were-- there were air-raid practices long before Germany was in the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Everybody had to have an air-raid shelter in their house, and we hadn't seen a city lit up-- well, when we first arrived in London, I suppose-- but in this whole year.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And here was New York City.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Our relatives who provided the affidavit for us, Mr. and Mrs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Kurt Blum of Philadelphia, picked us up at the ship.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Blum's father-in-law, his name was Moses Lieberman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And at the time, a vice president of Snellenburg's department store here was an additional sponsor, since Mr.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Blum's sponsorship was not enough, financially, to sustain us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The relationship, officially, was that Mr.-- that my parents were Mr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Blum's aunt and uncle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Basically, not quite, my mother's sister had married into the family of Mr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Blum's mother.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And so they were really just in-laws, indirectly, [INAUDIBLE], as we would say.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "However, when Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Blum was still young and his father passed away in Germany, in the '20s, my mother spent a whole year in his house to help his mother get ready to emigrate to the States, because at that time, already, she had several brothers here who wanted her to come over, since she was widowed.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "This was the Heidelberger family who, for a long period of time, had a chocolate factory here in Philadelphia, Brothers Heidelberger Chocolates.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And so it was, perhaps, a favor repaid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And perhaps it was simply because they wanted to help, but it will never stop being grateful to the Blums for helping us to come to this country.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "If it weren't for them, we wouldn't be here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I wouldn't be here, and my children wouldn't be here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we first came here, we came to Philadelphia right away.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
